00:51:52.530 --> 00:51:56.300
But it plays some signals,
some sounds in your ears.

00:51:56.300 --> 00:51:59.420
And apparently it's supposed
to divert your state

00:51:59.420 --> 00:52:01.010
to what's the flow state.

